      • connectToServerUsingProtocol

        private static boolean connectToServerUsingProtocol​(java.lang.String ipAndPort)
        Connects to the given server (IP and Port) using an empty (no) password. Other than GTAController#connectToServer(String) and GTAController#connectToServer(String, String), this method uses the samp:// protocol to connect to make the samp launcher connect to the server.
        Parameters:
        ipAndPort - the server to connect to
        Returns:
        true if it was most likely successful

      • connectToServer

        public static void connectToServer​(java.lang.String address,
                                   java.lang.Integer port,
                                   java.lang.String password)
        Connects to the given server (IP and Port) using the given password. Uses the commandline to open samp and connect to the server.
        Parameters:
        address - server address
        port - server port
        password - the password to use for connecting
